#This map is made for those who like to make videos for previewing skins or just custom model testing.

I made this a while back and completely forgot about it. I touched it up a little more and optimized it a bit, so now it's good for a release. Most of the brushwork is world (not tied to entity) mainly because there's no need for bots, and it's not a competitive gameplay map.
There is a very good chance that every thing in this map is inaccurate to what a shooting range probably looks like nowadays. This is just what I had envisioned, so that's how it came out.

Sorry about a couple of the custom textures and their mipmaplessness. I tried for like a half hour to get them mipmapped and for some reason they just wouldn't work. 

Install into your maps folder

If you find Chef Ainsley, that means you are a noclippin' fool. jk <3
